data.name: xrLabel15.Text
data.value: You are liable for any damage howsoever caused to the allocated room(s) or to the Pension House premises or property caused by you or any persons in your party (whether or not staying at the Pension House) during your stay. Optimum Pension House reserves the right to refuse accommodation to you or any person(s) without any notice and terminate any booking without being liable for any refund or compensation for the following reasons:

data.name: xrLabel13.Text
data.value: If you check-out beyond the stipulated time, Optimum Pension House reserves the right, without further notice to you, to charge you an additional 12-hour stay at the then prevailing room rate or remove your belongings into the front desk and deny you further access into the room. Optimum Pension House shall not be liable for any loss or damage to your belongings as a result of the action(s) taken.

data.name: xrLabel11.Text
data.value: Payment equivalent to a one-day stay must be made upon check-in. The Guest must present a valid Identification Card with photo upon check-in. The Guest named in the Guest Information Sheet must be the person staying at the Pension House. Otherwise, we reserve the right to refuse accommodation.

data.name: xrLabel8.Text
data.value: Room rates and details are correct at the time of publication and are subject to change without notice. Optimum Pension House observes a strict NO SMOKING, NO LIQUOR policy. Failure to comply with this policy entitles us to impose penalties (PhP 1,000.00) and/or terminate your booking and stay at the Pension House at our sole discretion and you must leave the Pension House premises immediately without compensation or reimbursement.
